<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Contact Us</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/ourServices">Our Services</a></li>
                <li><a href="/contactUs">Contact Us</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="contact">
        <div class="contact_sec">
            <h1>Contact Us</h1>
            <p>Thank you for your interest in our services! We would love to hear from you and answer any questions you
                may have.
                Please fill out the form below with your contact information and message, and we will get back to you as
                soon as possible. Alternatively, you can reach us by phone or email listed on the right-hand side of the
                page</p>
            <form>
                <label for="name">Name:</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name"><br>

                <label for="subject">Subject:</label>
                <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject"><br>

                <label for="email">Email:</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email"><br>

                <label for="message">Message:</label>
                <textarea id="message" name="message"></textarea><br>

                <button id="submit" type="submit">Submit</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>